#
# Regional sites and Public Services
# Reminder on federal subjects naming:
# | English name        | RU transliteration    | RU naming         |
# | Region, Province    | Oblast                | Область           |
# | Territory           | Krai                  | Край              |
# | Autonomous Region,  | Avtonomniy Okrug      | Автономный Округ  |
# | Autonomous Area     |                       |                   |
#
# Moscow, St. Petersburg, Sevastopol — are separate federal subjects,
# meaning that e.g. Moscow is not part of Moscow Region.
#

